Zineb Oukach (Arabic; /ˈziːnɛb ˈuːkəʃ/; a mụrụ na Disemba 1, 1982) bụ onye Morocco na-eme ihe nkiri na ihe nlereanya, nke ndị na-ege ntị n'ụwa niile maara maka ịrụ ọrụ Fatima na 2007 Gavin Hood film Rendition
A mụrụ Oukach ma zụlite ya na Casablanca, Morocco
N'afọ 2004, ọ kwagara France, ebe ọ gụrụ Economics tupu ọ gaa Cours Florent iji lekwasị anya n'ọrụ ime ihe nkiri ya.

A maara ya nke ọma na Morocco maka ọrụ ya na Parfum de Mer, site n'aka onye na-eme ihe nkiri Moroccan a ma ama Abdelhai Laraki, na maka ọrụ ya n'usoro ihe nkiri telivishọn Moroccan Une Famille Respectable nke Kamal Kamal, na 2007 Oukach ghọrọ onye ama ama n'ụwa niile maka arụmọrụ ya dịka onye Arab na-eto eto na-eduga na ihe nkiri Rendition na Meryl Streep, yana Jake Gyllenhaal na Reese Witherspoon
Oukach rụkwara ọrụ na The Wolf of Wall Street Na usoro ihe nkiri telivishọn sayensị akụkọ ifo Alien Dawn, nke a na-egosi na Nickelodeon.
